{"body": "It could have separate formatters that are passed to the `format` method. So instead of calling\r\n\r\n```ruby\r\nformat(..., :html)\r\n```\r\n\r\nYou could then inject the formatter:\r\n\r\n```ruby\r\nformat(... HTMLFormatter.new)\r\n```\r\n\r\nOr use the other way around:\r\n\r\n```ruby\r\nHTMLFormatter.new(inspector.collect_all_routes(_routes.routes)).format.\r\n```", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/11329248", "created_at": "2012-12-13T10:16:35Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/8499#issuecomment-11329248", "updated_at": "2012-12-13T10:16:35Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 8499, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/carlosantoniodasilva", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/77237b97a465ae5a293ad323b7296837?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F60b997fd68261ce70cadaf6c8226c042.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/received_events", "gravatar_id": "77237b97a465ae5a293ad323b7296837", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "carlosantoniodasilva", "type": "User", "id": 26328, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237f2a1bd3543c15100a66f"}, "id": 11329248, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/8499"}
